descr: "The details of a healthcare service available at a location."

fields.name: daysOfWeek
fields.descr: "Indicates which days of the week are available between the start and end Times."

fields.name: allDay
fields.descr: "Is this always available? (hence times are irrelevant) e.g. 24 hour service."

fields.name: availableStartTime
fields.descr: "The opening time of day. Note: If the AllDay flag is set, then this time is ignored."

fields.name: availableEndTime
fields.descr: "The closing time of day. Note: If the AllDay flag is set, then this time is ignored."
